        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li>
            <span class="ba-num">01</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Demand a published output number — and a monthly minimum guarantee</h4>
              <p>"We'll write content for you" means nothing. "30 articles per month minimum or you get the next month free" means everything. If the vendor won't commit, that's the answer.</p>
